    "longBusinessSummary": "PetroVietnam General Services Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in distribution, supply chain, catering, and property services businesses in Vietnam. The company operates through Electronic Products; Wholesale Business; and Other Products and Services segments. It trades in plastic resins, textile fibers, fertilizers, pesticides, chemicals, and telecommunication equipment; sells supplies, office equipment, and audio-visual equipment; provides support and management, and human resources services; and leases warehouse, workshops, premises, and offices. The company also develops, trades, and manages real estate properties, including office, hotels, residential projects, etc.; supplies specialized materials and equipment in the oil and gas industry; and provides heavy transportation and lifting, liquified petroleum gas trading and distribution, and gas filling services. In addition, it is involved distribution of computer, electronics, components, peripheral devices, and software; retail of mobile phones; trading of electronic devices, and refrigeration and electronic household appliances; wholesale of solid, liquid, and gaseous fuels and related products; and packing services for paper products. PetroVietnam General Services Joint Stock Company was founded in 1996 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
